title: Texans lose their minds, trade everyone - Bonus Pod (Football 9/1)
description:
The EIGHTH podcast of the week features Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough breaking down the insane action from the NFL Saturday, including the Texans trading Jadeveon Clowney to the Seahawks and trading for Laremy Tunsil. Then the guys break down other notable roster cuts and discuss the buzz surrounding Ezekiel Elliott's new deal and Melvin Gordon's situation.
